attention difficulty, school is an environment

00:00:56.236 --> 00:00:58.466 align:middle
where it really demands you
to be paying attention a lot.

00:00:58.846 --> 00:01:02.046 align:middle
And when you have a disability, a lot of
times you're thinking of other things,

00:01:02.046 --> 00:01:04.416 align:middle
